dc_title_s: Somerset County, New Jersey highways 1962 map 6
dc_description_s: Base map of Somerset County. Sheet six of a six sheet map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. This sheet includes four of the series' 12 insets of major road junctures. State highways are as of July 1961.|Large tear in the left center of map.
